modName: Superset contain all the unique armor and weapon
summary: A simple mod : type bat superset in the console and all the uniques weapons and armors will appear in your inventory.
descriptionHtml:
A simple mod : type bat superset in the console and all the uniques weapons and armors will appear in your inventory.

How to install :Put the file in your skyrim data folder

How to uninstall : Delete the superset file from your data folder
